6	//! tool results, meta/system/sidechain lines, and bookkeeping
7	//! entry types. Reveal flags: `--thinking`, `--tools`, `--meta`.
8	//! A trailing summary line always reports what was hidden or
9	//! skipped. Malformed lines (e.g. a live session's truncated
10	//! last line) warn to stderr and never fail the run.
